Package temp.fibHeap.stixar.graph.paths Description

Path related structures and algorithms, including shortests paths.

This package contains a path class and shortests paths algorithms. A plethora of static shortest paths methods are available via the stixar.graph.paths.SSSP and stixar.graph.paths.APSP methods.

In addition, this package contains a plethora of shortests paths algorithms, one for each case with a different complexity class.
